  "title": "关于规范招聘市场秩序的倡议书",
  "content": "<div class=\"rich_media_content js_underline_content autoTypeSetting24psection\" id=\"js_content\">\n <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\">\n  <section data-role=\"paragraph\">\n   <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\">\n    <section data-role=\"paragraph\">\n     <section data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\">\n      <section data-role=\"paragraph\">\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height: 1.5em;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.2px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\">\n          <span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n           全体行业同仁、广大用户朋友：\n          </span>\n         </span>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height: 1.5em;\">\n        <span leaf=\"\">\n         <br/>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height: 1.5em;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.2px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\">\n          <span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n           就业，关乎每一个家庭的万家灯火，每一次选择与被选择，都承载着具体的生活与深切的希望。构建一个真实、高效、友善的求职招聘环境，是我们求职者和招聘方的共同心愿，也是BOSS直聘矢志不渝的真诚努力。\n          </span>\n         </span>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height: 1.5em;\">\n        <span leaf=\"\">\n         <br/>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height: 1.5em;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.2px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\">\n          <span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n           在此，我们郑重承诺，BOSS直聘将始终秉持“用户至上，服务就业”的核心理念，持续升级企业资质与岗位信息的审核力度，对任何虚假招聘行为绝不姑息，坚决打击。同时，我们将不断完善公开透明的服务规则，及时回应用户诉求，充分保障用户权益。\n          </span>\n         </span>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height: 1.5em;\">\n        <span leaf=\"\">\n         <br/>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height: 1.5em;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.2px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\">\n          <span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n           行业的繁荣发展，离不开所有参与者的携手共建。为此，我们怀着诚挚之心，向全体行业同仁、广大用户朋友发出以下倡议：\n          </span>\n         </span>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height: 1.5em;\">\n        <span leaf=\"\">\n         <br/>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height: 1.5em;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.2px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\">\n          <span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n           我们倡议行业同仁，主动扛起主体责任。在严格遵守法律法规的基础上，积极提升服务标准；在完善内部管理机制的同时，推动运营规则的公开透明；在追求商业价值增长之际，深植促进就业的社会责任。我们倡议行业同仁，携手共进，建立健全行业信用评价体系，形成高效有力的行业自律长效机制，共同为营造一个健康、诚信、充满活力的招聘生态贡献力量。\n          </span>\n         </span>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height: 1.5em;\">\n        <span leaf=\"\">\n         <br/>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height: 1.5em;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.2px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\">\n          <span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n           我们倡议招聘方发布真实的职位信息，求职者提供真实的个人履历。在每一次沟通交流中，让我们多一分理解，多一分尊重。同时，我们热切呼吁广大用户，积极参与平台治理，主动监督举报虚假信息和违规行为，共同筑牢诚信防线。\n          </span>\n         </span>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height: 1.5em;\">\n        <span leaf=\"\">\n         <br/>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:justify;line-height: 1.5em;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.2px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\">\n          <span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n           独行快，众行远。我们坚信，通过平台用心自律、行业开放共建、社会广泛监督的有机结合，互联网招聘行业必将迈向一个更加规范、更加透明、更加高效的新阶段。\n          </span>\n         </span>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"line-height:1.5em;\">\n        <span leaf=\"\">\n         <br/>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:right;line-height: 1.5em;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.2px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\">\n          <span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n           BOSS直聘\n          </span>\n         </span>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:right;line-height: 1.5em;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1.2px;\">\n         <span leaf=\"\">\n          <span style=\"font-size: 17px;\" textstyle=\"\">\n           2025年6月26日\n          </span>\n         </span>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n       <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 1.5em;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\">\n        <span leaf=\"\">\n         <br/>\n        </span>\n       </p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n </section>\n <p style=\"display: none;\">\n  <mp-style-type data-value=\"3\">\n  </mp-style-type>\n </p>\n</div>\n",
